-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Refactoring Goals:

* separated GUI from function
* users can register callbacks for various events

2. dump results as TestNG compatible XML file

3. set functionality on top on tcltest, i.e. with interface and behavior
   compatibility (might not be necessary, depends on timing tests)
3.1. check if timing on capturing events produces acceptable results
3.2. do not produce timing information when converting existing tcltest log files

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
API:
tclunit::configure callbacks
tclunit::run_tests path
tclunit::stop_tests

Events for callbacks:
<init>
<property> name value
<suite> filename
<skipped> filename testcase reason
<start> filename testcase
<passed> filename testcase ?time?
<failed> filename testcase report ?time?
<status> filename #passed #skipped #failed
<total> #passed #skipped #failed #time
<error> filename report

